import './navbar.css'

function Navbar() {
    return ( <
        div class = "navbar" >

        <
        div id = "nav-right" >
        <
        img src = { require("./assets/Icon.png").default }
        alt = "Icon" / >
        <
        /div> <div id = "nav-left" > <
        button id = "login"> Login < /button>  <
        button id = "register" > Register < /button>  < /
        div > <
        /div>
    );
}

export default Navbar
